FIFA WORLD CUP Section::::2006 FIFA World Cup . Tunisia drew their opening game against Saudi Arabia 2–2 , but lost their second match to Spain 3–1 and lost their last group match to Ukraine 1–0 , ending their 2006 FIFA World Cup campaign .
